
## Claude Code notes

- The shared, cross-agent instructions live in `AGENTS.md`, imported on the first
  line above. Edit `AGENTS.md`, not this block — this block is regenerated by ai-dev-kit.
- For codebase questions, prefer `graphify query "<question>"` when
  `graphify-out/graph.json` exists; fall back to reading source only if needed.
- After modifying code, run `graphify update .` to keep the graph current.
- Model and permissions for this project are pinned in `.claude/settings.json`.
